=== Education_Approach ===
Education programs teaching digital literacy:
• How to evaluate sources
• Recognizing manipulation and misinformation
• When to ask for help
• Critical thinking about online content
• Healthy digital habits

These address the actual goal: helping parents protect their children. No surveillance infrastructure, no privacy risks, no one-size-fits-all policies.

