=== Parent_Responsibility ===
True. But laws don't fix that.

A parent who won't install parental controls also won't prevent their kid from using a VPN. A parent who isn't involved won't be helped by age verification laws.

The difference? These solutions don't create surveillance infrastructure that can be misused. They empower parents without endangering everyone's privacy.

